<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-black/40">Last updated: June 2026</p>

  <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none space-y-6 text-black/70">

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">1. Who we are</h2>
      <p>Publisher (<strong>socialpost.urlyapp.com</strong>) is a personal social media management tool that allows users to schedule and publish content to connected social media platforms. It is operated for personal and testing use.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">2. Data we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
        <li><strong>Account data:</strong> email address and hashed password used to log in to Publisher.</li>
        <li><strong>OAuth tokens:</strong> access and refresh tokens issued by connected platforms (Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, TikTok, Pinterest) to act on your behalf. Tokens are encrypted at rest.</li>
        <li><strong>Media files:</strong> images and videos you upload for publishing.</li>
        <li><strong>Post content:</strong> captions, titles, and scheduling information you enter.</li>
        <li><strong>Session data:</strong> a session identifier stored in a cookie to keep you logged in.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">3. How we use your data</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
        <li>To authenticate you and maintain your session.</li>
        <li>To publish content to social media platforms on your behalf using your OAuth tokens.</li>
        <li>To store your media and post history for your own reference.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-2">We do not sell, share, or transfer your data to third parties for advertising or marketing purposes.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">4. Third-party platforms</h2>
      <p>When you connect a social media account, you authorise Publisher to interact with that platform's API on your behalf. Each platform has its own privacy policy:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
        <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/privacy/policy/" class="text-mint underline" target="_blank">Meta (Facebook &amp; Instagram)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-mint underline" target="_blank">Google (YouTube)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.tiktok.com/legal/page/us/privacy-policy/en" class="text-mint underline" target="_blank">TikTok</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://policy.pinterest.com/privacy-policy" class="text-mint underline" target="_blank">Pinterest</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">5. Data retention</h2>
      <p>Your data is retained for as long as your account is active. You may delete your account and all associated data at any time by submitting a deletion request (see section 6).</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">6. Your rights &amp; data deletion</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To request deletion of your data, visit our <a href="/data-deletion" class="text-mint underline">Data Deletion</a> page.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">7. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use a single session cookie (<code>connect.sid</code>) to keep you logged in. No tracking or advertising cookies are used.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">8. Security</h2>
      <p>OAuth tokens are encrypted before being stored in the database. Connections are served over HTTPS.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">9. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related questions or data requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@urlyapp.com" class="text-mint underline">contact@urlyapp.com</a>.</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
